Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.90,0:00:15.30,Defaul,,0000,0000,0000,,翻译:basaka[dmhy]，校对:kire[popgo]、SORA[popgo]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.71,0:00:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不错  速濑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.78,0:00:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,状态不错嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.36,0:00:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了这个感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.93,0:00:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个成绩的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.97,0:00:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  这么心神不宁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.50,0:00:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什...什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.54,0:00:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,7分  5分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.93,0:00:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,6分  4分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.14,0:00:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3分  5分  7分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.04,0:00:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总计37分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.12,0:00:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离合格还差得很远啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.37,0:01:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你突然冒出来算什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.26,0:01:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,37分又是什么东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.11,0:01:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  孝之君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.02,0:01:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.12,0:01:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...难道说...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.00,0:01:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...我妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.33,0:01:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是凉宫茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.86,0:01:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照  鸣海孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.59,0:01:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道今天她也和我们一起？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.31,0:01:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.30,0:01:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想她只是跟来...而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.57,0:01:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.71,0:01:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是暑假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.50,0:01:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我也不会闲到来打扰两位火热的约会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.33,0:01:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火热...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.58,0:01:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜你真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.42,0:01:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我去泳池了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.27,0:01:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在还不能“吃了”姐姐哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.05,0:01:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  脸红了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.90,0:01:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是纯情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.43,0:01:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.53,0:01:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这...这...这个臭小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.56,0:01:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  孝之君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.87,0:02:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜又说了什么奇怪的话吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.12,0:02:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.79,0:02:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜一直这么活蹦乱跳的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.97,0:02:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...有点过头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.95,0:02:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.02,0:02:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜的腔调有点像速濑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.49,0:02:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.13,0:02:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个...茜也是游泳部的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.89,0:02:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.38,0:02:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  还参加过大会得过奖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.88,0:02:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说是以水月为目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.28,0:02:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天哪  前途险恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.40,0:02:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.71,0:02:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.12,0:02:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚没睡吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.29,0:02:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在玩慎二借给我的游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.58,0:02:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果就早上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.75,0:02:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  这样对身体不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.13,0:02:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学习上怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.80,0:02:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马马虎虎吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.57,0:03:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之君也考白陵大多好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.40,0:03:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,港阳大太远了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.78,0:03:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白陵大的话又近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又能一起上学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.75,0:03:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始努力的话  一定...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.10,0:03:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以孝之君也考白陵大...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.79,0:03:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐过头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.10,0:03:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时叫醒我就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.10,0:03:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是孝之君睡得很香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.93,0:03:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表情很可爱  就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.51,0:03:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.17,0:03:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.23,0:03:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我带来了好东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.27,0:03:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找个地方坐下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.91,0:04:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  没有碎掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦~~  肉馅饼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.74,0:04:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来很好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.83,0:04:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我听说孝之君喜欢吃肉馅饼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.80,0:04:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  其实很早以前就开始试着做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直做不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.23,0:04:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的也有点不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.34,0:04:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好吃的话就直说  不要勉强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.77,0:04:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦  我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.90,0:04:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.26,0:04:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.00,0:04:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.64,0:04:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.38,0:04:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.86,0:04:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也吃吃看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.50,0:04:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的  这次做好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.50,0:04:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.12,0:05:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.39,0:05:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.08,0:05:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.45,0:05:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的  所以今天...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.00,0:05:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.44,0:05:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话  上来坐坐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.13,0:05:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.71,0:05:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会觉得不自在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.54,0:05:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...没有这回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.15,0:05:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.51,0:05:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.98,0:05:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  肚子饿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.02,0:06:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么  快点上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.15,0:06:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进来还是不进来  哪个？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.53,0:06:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3，2，1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.06,0:06:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.60,0:06:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...已经是晚上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.40,0:06:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然来打扰未免太失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.60,0:06:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.79,0:06:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别在意那种事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等...等等  茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.44,0:06:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了  带客人来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.38,0:06:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.94,0:06:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣海君  不用这么紧张啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.45,0:06:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.89,0:06:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来  不要客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.92,0:06:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不够的话尽管说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.46,0:06:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再为你做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.16,0:06:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.98,0:06:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.48,0:06:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜  你玩够没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.92,0:06:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思  孝之君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.50,0:07:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了  茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.48,0:07:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.65,0:07:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚刚在想 H 的事情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.73,0:07:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个...真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.77,0:07:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.89,0:07:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  奇怪吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.78,0:07:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...倒不是奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.49,0:07:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想有个哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.41,0:07:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看起来有点靠不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.44,0:07:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就凑合着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.71,0:07:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.07,0:07:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以  哥哥你一定要和姐姐结婚哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.83,0:07:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜  你在说什么啊  真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.21,0:07:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了  将来的事先不说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣海君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.07,0:08:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交往的时候可要好好对待遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.03,0:08:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.60,0:08:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.59,0:08:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天的夏祭没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.33,0:08:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.02,0:08:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  父母同意延长门限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.86,0:08:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是水月说有事不能来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.71,0:08:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.87,0:08:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是交了男朋友了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.78,0:08:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是吗  原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.71,0:08:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.64,0:08:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月说她有男朋友了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.06,0:08:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才不能来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.67,0:08:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.49,0:08:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜说在街上看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.30,0:08:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她和一个男人走在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.02,0:08:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那明天就我们两个去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.10,0:08:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慎二么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.53,0:08:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不去管他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.38,0:08:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样对待平君不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.19,0:08:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.02,0:08:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那明天见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.52,0:08:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.09,0:09:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是鸣海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.66,0:09:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在不在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.77,0:09:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有事的话请听到提示音后留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.64,0:09:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速濑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.32,0:09:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天为什么不接电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你重新打过来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.92,0:09:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为我不在的时候你打了3次来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.62,0:10:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.11,0:10:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能听我说吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.03,0:10:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是有关男朋友的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.57,0:10:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有男朋友呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.05,0:10:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.27,0:10:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是在一起而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.41,0:10:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是昨天他向我表白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.91,0:10:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那交往吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.64,0:10:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得该怎么办好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.55,0:10:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你问我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.55,0:10:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己的选择的话我会支持你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.49,0:10:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.20,0:10:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.70,0:10:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说虽然不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.28,0:10:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是第10个向我表白的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.70,0:11:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是都被我甩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.68,0:11:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这算是在自夸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.07,0:11:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  小心我扁你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.00,0:11:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都称赞我的头发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.27,0:11:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我却很讨厌它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.38,0:11:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这头长发代表了那个讨厌的固执的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.94,0:11:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今没有称赞过它的只有一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.09,0:11:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说还是短发适合我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.06,0:11:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...对那个人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.26,0:11:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.14,0:11:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种事我自己也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.44,0:11:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决定了  这次也不交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.48,0:11:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想象遥一样正视自己的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.64,0:11:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  这样也不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.58,0:12:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏祭...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.74,0:12:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗  你和遥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.85,0:12:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法  过会儿去道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.30,0:12:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.35,0:12:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慎二  遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.56,0:12:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之  你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.07,0:12:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明说今天两个人去看夏祭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.53,0:12:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么把凉宫一个人扔在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.96,0:12:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她还担心你不来了一直在哭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.99,0:12:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了  平君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.13,0:12:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.19,0:12:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.30,0:12:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你们约好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.50,0:12:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我想找他谈心拉他来这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.08,0:12:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近出了点事  所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.31,0:12:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.43,0:12:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.24,0:12:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然觉得对不起遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.39,0:12:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是水月的事也不能不管吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.20,0:12:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.09,0:12:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样  没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.18,0:12:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为水月是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.94,0:12:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.04,0:12:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.44,0:13:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.44,0:13:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家最终还是聚在这里了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.92,0:13:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友伙伴就是这样的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.26,0:13:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.37,0:13:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  难得大家都在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.04,0:13:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来去看夏祭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.22,0:13:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就算谢罪我来请客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.99,0:13:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.20,0:13:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前先一起拍一张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.64,0:13:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.97,0:13:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4个人一起拍照还是第一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.95,0:13:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.76,0:13:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以留作纪念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.15,0:13:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再靠过来一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.19,0:13:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.10,0:13:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.98,0:13:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.12,0:13:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月很烦恼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.13,0:13:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我也会这么做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.46,0:13:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.45,0:14:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以孝之君能这么关心水月  我很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.41,0:14:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他们出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.71,0:14:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜也一起去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.41,0:14:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.85,0:14:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上来坐一会儿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还想和你再聊聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是遥的房间啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.50,0:14:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会不好意思的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.97,0:14:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这么盯着看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.91,0:14:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好多连环画呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.08,0:14:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.00,0:14:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.85,0:14:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时的连环画《玛雅乌尔的礼物》
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.12,0:14:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那本书没有吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.85,0:14:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那下次两个人一起去找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.40,0:14:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦想是将来成为连环画作家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.49,0:14:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以上了大学想专攻儿童心理学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.03,0:14:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.39,0:15:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定会实现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.22,0:15:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候把我们4人的故事写进去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.28,0:15:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.34,0:15:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.65,0:16:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.72,0:16:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.02,0:16:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.75,0:16:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.44,0:16:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们回来了啊  真晚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.07,0:16:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.02,0:16:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难不成你把姐姐“吃”了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.07,0:16:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜你在胡说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.14,0:16:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太可疑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.86,0:16:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.14,0:16:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是要妨碍我还是支持我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.28,0:16:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.69,0:16:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.18,0:17:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天真对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.08,0:17:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.98,0:17:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有必要着急的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.38,0:17:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有的是时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.20,0:17:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之君  我们来念咒语吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.10,0:17:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.06,0:17:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样重复我的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.05,0:17:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如同无限夜空中的闪烁群星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.96,0:17:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的心交织在一起不分离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.12,0:17:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使两人无法牵手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.70,0:17:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我们依然牢记……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.84,0:18:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之君也考白陵大多好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.81,0:18:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人  真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.11,0:18:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要考白陵大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.88,0:18:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在说要考  你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.81,0:18:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还真是乐观啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.78,0:18:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凉宫吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.15,0:18:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.71,0:18:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  迟到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.45,0:18:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥要生气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.04,0:18:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...有了这个就会原谅我了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.17,0:18:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.93,0:18:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.63,0:18:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速濑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.16,0:18:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这身打扮算什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.99,0:18:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约会吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.01,0:19:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  参观职业队啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.17,0:19:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.60,0:19:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这口气什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.64,0:19:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢  和遥约会？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.35,0:19:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在柊町站前碰面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.62,0:19:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们相处得不错嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.13,0:19:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真令人羡慕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.48,0:19:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好说好说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.56,0:19:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.61,0:19:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之  那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.74,0:19:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实今天是我的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.16,0:19:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.68,0:19:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.47,0:19:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戒指吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.59,0:19:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.68,0:19:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生日礼物要戒指...你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.02,0:19:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也对  对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.61,0:19:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么...我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.52,0:19:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗  但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.35,0:20:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送你不想要的东西你也不会高兴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.01,0:20:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大出血...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.48,0:20:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之  谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.89,0:20:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好珍惜它的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.21,0:20:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我的生日时我要你10倍奉还
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.85,0:20:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.01,0:20:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.71,0:20:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交通事故吗  真危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.55,0:21:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥...会不会生气回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.21,0:21:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是个女孩子吧  好惨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.49,0:21:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.09,0:21:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被车撞倒了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.85,0:21:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在等人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.36,0:21:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.11,0:21:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.24,0:21:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.28,0:21:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.85,0:21:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.42,0:21:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让让...对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.91,0:21:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.28,0:21:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪儿  遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.00,0:21:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.05,0:21:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本日14点15分发生事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.19,0:21:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从遗留的学生证照片确认是本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.20,0:21:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被害者姓名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.44,0:22:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白陵大附属柊学园  3年级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.15,0:22:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凉宫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.18,0:22:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.57,0:22:33.51,dmhy2,,0000,0000,0000,,站在溫柔的微風中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.57,0:22:33.51,dmhy,,0000,0000,0000,,やわらかな風に抱かれ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.59,0:22:41.96,dmhy2,,0000,0000,0000,,思念著你使我心痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.59,0:22:41.96,dmhy,,0000,0000,0000,,あなた想う心　切なくなる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.66,0:22:48.01,dmhy2,,0000,0000,0000,,一個人站在山丘上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.66,0:22:48.01,dmhy,,0000,0000,0000,,丘のうえひとりきりで
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.74,0:22:55.17,dmhy2,,0000,0000,0000,,目送著季節的逝去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.74,0:22:55.17,dmhy,,0000,0000,0000,,季節見送っているの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.59,0:23:02.61,dmhy2,,0000,0000,0000,,遙望青空的彼岸可以看見什麽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.59,0:23:02.61,dmhy,,0000,0000,0000,,青空の向こう  何がみえるのかな
